Ruby/GTK2
=========
Ruby/GTK2 is a Ruby binding of GTK+2.0.x.

Requirements
------------
   Ruby: http://www.ruby-lang.org/
   GTK+: http://www.gtk.org/
   Ruby/GLib2: http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.net/

Install
-------
   0. install ruby-1.6.x, GTK+-2.0.x, Ruby/GLib2.
   1. ruby extconf.rb
   2. make
   3. su
   4. make install

